// Remove: import type { MockServer } from '../tests/test-server.js';
```

## REFACTOR
- Ensure all shared types are in proper type files
- Add CI check for test imports in production code

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] No production code imports from tests/
- [ ] Types properly shared between prod and test
- [ ] Build still works
- [ ] Tests still pass

## Problem
Silent error suppression in TypeScript core makes debugging impossible:
- `src/rpc.ts:520` - `try { this.abort(err); } catch (err2) {}`
- `src/rpc.ts:601` - `.catch(err => {});`
- `src/map.ts:168` - `result.catch(err => {});`

## RED (Write failing tests first)
```typescript
